Getting parameters information using partial search words

Source: R/get_param_info.R
get_param_data_df.Rd

Getting parameters information using partial search words

get_param_data_df(
  parameter = NULL,
  file_path = NULL,
  version = "last",
  kind = "all",
  exact = FALSE
)

Arguments

parameter

Optional name or partial name or a vector of
file_path

Optional, xml file path or a vector of
version

Optional, Stics version (default value, "last") Only the 2 last are referenced: V9.0, V9.1
kind

Kind of information to be retrieved for parameters among "parameter", "formalism" or "all" for both of them
exact

Logical, if TRUE, the exact name is searched

Value

A data.frame containing parameters names and their origin (file name), and their bounds or the formalism they belong to, or both of them.

Details

If not any name vector of names, information are extracted for all the existing parameters
